Her first child God decided to give her & Massie 2 identical princesses 😍😍& I cannot wait to shower them with love. 🫶🏽

My baby, The Art of Being Fly..
55 pages of game and a few quick stories on how I fell in love with fashion & how I stayed the flyest even when I was broke… get ya copy today on Amazon the link is in my bio✨
November 1st we celebrate National Authors Day 🥂 Support a indie author this week in fact try to support a few! Salute to all authors & future authors putting it all on the line for the love of words & their power. 
I see you. We need you. Keep writing.

📍PHILLY - Tuesday, November 21st Ima be in ya city spitting poems like my name is Jilly!!! 🤪 
I am so excited to be performing for @voicesinpower_ at @worldcafelive this show will be epic! I’ll be channeling my inner @missjillscott for the night with my own womenfesto 😏 TRUST this is a show you don’t wanna miss! Get your tickets bc this will again be a Sold Out! The link is in my bio!

📍Rochester - come out & hear me & some of Rochester’s most talented wordsmiths bare our souls on Sunday, December 3rd as @sunny__alicia presents Turning Pain into Poems @thelabcrcroc doors open at 6:30 pm Words start Flowin at 7 pm this is a dress to EXPRESS event! Link for tickets in my bio

Tuesday’s look details :
I’m getting a lot of inquiries but this isn’t a jumpsuit I got the leggings from @zara like 7 years ago, then grabbed the body suit and arm piece from @forever21 a few hrs before show time, thank God I packed my Tabi’s, my friend @nivenski freaked my hair in like 45 minutes & my face was beat by Me using all @elf products, except no foundation I used this bb cream/tinted moisturizer from @maybelline and boom! #TheArtOfBeingFly
